4343  /*!
4344  * \brief Interpolate variables to a coarser grid level.
4345  * \note Halo values are not communicated in this function.
4346  * \param[in] geoFine - Fine grid.
4347  * \param[in] varsFine - Matrix of variables on the fine grid.
4348  * \param[in] geoCoarse - Coarse grid.
4349  * \param[in] varsCoarse - Matrix of variables interpolated to the coarse grid.
4350  */
4351  inline static void MultigridRestriction(const CGeometry& geoFine, const su2activematrix& varsFine,
4352  const CGeometry& geoCoarse, su2activematrix& varsCoarse) {
4353  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(roundUpDiv(geoCoarse.GetnPointDomain(), omp_get_num_threads()))
4354  for (auto iPointCoarse = 0ul; iPointCoarse < geoCoarse.GetnPointDomain(); ++iPointCoarse) {
4355 
4356  for (auto iVar = 0ul; iVar < varsCoarse.cols(); iVar++) {
4357  varsCoarse(iPointCoarse, iVar) = 0.0;
4358  }
4359  const su2double scale = 1 / geoCoarse.nodes->GetVolume(iPointCoarse);
4360 
4361  for (auto iChildren = 0ul; iChildren < geoCoarse.nodes->GetnChildren_CV(iPointCoarse); ++iChildren) {
4362  const auto iPointFine = geoCoarse.nodes->GetChildren_CV(iPointCoarse, iChildren);
4363  const su2double w = geoFine.nodes->GetVolume(iPointFine) * scale;
4364  for (auto iVar = 0ul; iVar < varsCoarse.cols(); ++iVar) {
4365  varsCoarse(iPointCoarse, iVar) += w * varsFine(iPointFine, iVar);
4366  }
4367  }
4368  }
4369  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
4370  }

4391  /*!
4392  * \brief "Add" residual at (iPoint,iVar) to residual variables local to the thread.
4393  * \param[in] iPoint - Point index.
4394  * \param[in] iVar - Variable index.
4395  * \param[in] res - Residual at (iPoint,iVar), e.g. LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar)
4396  * \param[in,out] resRMS - increases by pow(Residual, 2)
4397  * \param[in,out] resMax - increases to max(resMax, Residual)
4398  * \param[in,out] idxMax - changes when resMax increases
4399  */
4400  static inline void ResidualReductions_PerThread(unsigned long iPoint, unsigned short iVar, su2double res, su2double* resRMS, su2double* resMax,
4401  unsigned long* idxMax) {
4402  res = fabs(res);
4403  resRMS[iVar] += res * res;
4404  if (res > resMax[iVar]) {
4405  resMax[iVar] = res;
4406  idxMax[iVar] = iPoint;
4407  }
4408  }
4409 
4410  /*!
4411  * \brief "Add" local residual variables of all threads to compute global residual variables.
4412  */
4413  inline void ResidualReductions_FromAllThreads(const CGeometry* geometry, const CConfig* config, const su2double* resRMS, const su2double* resMax,
4414  const unsigned long* idxMax){
4415  SetResToZero();
4416 
4417  SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
4418  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4419  Residual_RMS[iVar] += resRMS[iVar];
4420  AddRes_Max(iVar, resMax[iVar], geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(idxMax[iVar]), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(idxMax[iVar]));
4421  }
4422  END_SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
4423  SU2_OMP_BARRIER
4424 
4425  /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
4426  SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
4427  }
4428 
4429  /*!
4430  * \brief Set the RMS and MAX residual to zero.
4431  */
4432  inline void SetResToZero() {
4433  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS {
4434  for (auto& r : Residual_RMS) r = 0;
4435  for (auto& r : Residual_Max) r = 0;
4436  for (auto& p : Point_Max) p = 0;
4437  }
4438  END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
4439  }

4441  /*!
4442  * \brief Adds the maximal residual, this is useful for the convergence history.
4443  * \param[in] val_var - Index of the variable.
4444  * \param[in] val_residual - Value of the residual to store in the position <i>val_var</i>.
4445  * \param[in] val_point - Value of the point index for the max residual.
4446  * \param[in] val_coord - Location (x, y, z) of the max residual point.
4447  */
4448  inline void AddRes_Max(unsigned short val_var,
4449  su2double val_residual,
4450  unsigned long val_point,
4451  const su2double* val_coord) {
4452  if (val_residual > Residual_Max[val_var]) {
4453  Residual_Max[val_var] = val_residual;
4454  Point_Max[val_var] = val_point;
4455  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4456  Point_Max_Coord[val_var][iDim] = val_coord[iDim];
4457  }
4458  }
